-- Formosa Fire-Damaged Refinery Unit May Take a Year to Restart, Times Says
-- Yu-Huay Sun
-- 2010-07-28T00:22:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/formosa-fire-damaged-refinery-unit-may-take-a-year-to-restart-times-says.html

          
          
             Formosa Petrochemical Corp.’s fire-
damaged residual desulfurization unit may take one year to
restart, the Commercial Times reported, citing an official from
Taiwan’s Labor Affairs Council.  
